data.description: BRING YOUR IDEAS! BRING YOUR HORSES, GOATS, CHICKENS! THIS PROPERTY IS SO VERSATLE AND CAN BE USED FOR SO MANY PURPOSES!! OUTSIDE CITY LIMITS. NO KNOWN RESTRICTIONS! PRIME LOCATION! NO HOA! 4.14 ACRES just outside City Limits in the FAST GROWING Fate, Royse City area! UNRESTRICTED LAND like this is getting harder to find! HUGE 40X50 - 2,000 SQUARE FOOT SHOP with 220 Electric and separate panel box, 16 ft Center Height, 14 ft Roll Up Door, water ran and ready to be connected. 1200 Square Foot BARN with 220 Electric and separate panel box. Greenhouse. All storage buildings convey! Fenced and Cross Fenced. Coop set up and ready for chickens! Open floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths. Washer, Dryer, and Fridge Included. HVAC Replaced 2023. FHA approved. Ag Exempt Application Filed. Just off Hwy 66 - Easy Access to Hwy I30 and quick commute to HWY 380. Close to Rockwall, Royse City, Greenville
